text:
Another comment gives two factoids for TWICE and Megan Thee Stallion. After some research, I can confirm these two and two more.
>Birth place and departure: Meg was born in San Antonio, Texas, and departed soon after her birth. Mina was born in San Antonio, Texas, and departed as a toddler. Neither one became a member of San Antonio society.
>Birthdate and Korean respect: Meg was born 1995.02.15; Nayeon was born 1995.09.22. Therefore, Meg is unnie to all TWICE. Inversely, Meg was not permitted into rap society until after her 21st birthday in 2016. Therefore, TWICE is sunbaenim to Meg.
>Denunciation by a man in the music business: Huang Ahn denounced  周(孫子)子瑜   Sally generating an apology/confession video. Meg also has a video describing her incident and subsequent adjudication. 
>Meg and TWICE were in-person, on-stage together for the Billboard magazine WOMEN-MUSIC AWARDS.
